The Driver for BME680 is from bosch-sensortec(BSEC fusion library), the version used here is 1.4.7.1,
You can download the driver from: https://www.bosch-sensortec.com/bst/support_tools/downloads/overview_downloads.
I delete BSEC fusion library in the code.
